Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.41,0:11:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,也许在灾变之前  你做的也是类似的工作\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You probably had a job like this before the world fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.71,0:11:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,要我猜  我会说\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}If I had to guess, I'd say
