Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.10,0:11:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,能评判现在的我们\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}from which to judge who we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.27,0:11:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你们在我们大脑尘封的记忆中搜索\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}So you poke around the dusty corners of our brains,
