Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.20,0:12:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这让我认为你们的流通货币是美元\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}which makes me believe your currency is the U.S. Dollar,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.16,0:12:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你们需要严格管控现钞的数量\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and that you need to strictly control the amount in circulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你们使用熟悉的钱  作为一种强大的心理策略\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You use familiar money as a powerful psychological tactic,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.08,0:12:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你们知道人们有多怀念过去的世界\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}because you know how desperately people miss the old world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.67,0:12:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你们想了解我们的能耐\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You want to understand what we're capable of
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.09,0:12:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,了解我们是能帮助你们的社区变大变强\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and whether we can enhance your community
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.97,0:12:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,还是只会白白浪费资源\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}or if we'd simply be a drain on resources.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.43,0:12:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,但真相是  你们也要证明自己存在的合理性\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}But the truth of it is, you need to justify your existence, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.18,0:12:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,因为如今一个能运走垃圾\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Because isn't it almost more valuable now
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.02,0:12:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,让街道远离疾病的人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}to have someone who can haul the trash
