Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,能写下无尽问题清单的人更有价值吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}than someone who can write endless lists of questions,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.65,0:12:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟到头来\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}given that at the end of the day,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.07,0:12:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你只能靠直觉来判断\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}you just need to rely on your gut instinct
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.78,0:12:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,坐在你对面的人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}about whether or not the person across from you
