Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.91,0:12:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,但你们都是循规蹈矩的人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}But you're both people that follow the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.37,0:13:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾是律师\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I was a lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.00,0:13:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢规矩\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I like rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.63,0:13:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这能给混乱带来秩序\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}They bring order to the chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.93,0:13:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这意味着你们需要我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Which means you need me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.14,0:13:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我有理由相信我的兄弟  一名胸外科医生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I have reason to believe my brother, a thoracic surgeon,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.89,0:13:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,就住在联邦  他正在找我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}is living at the Commonwealth and is looking for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.69,0:13:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望我的团队获得加急评估\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'd like expedited processing for my group,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.77,0:13:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,依据你们社区的庇护和移民政策\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}as per your community's asylum and immigration policies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.65,0:13:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪里上的学来着\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Where did you go to school again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.40,0:13:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,牛津大学念的本科  在哈佛念的法学博士\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Undergraduate at Oxford, JD is from Harvard,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.70,0:13:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经很清楚了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}which you very well know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你想让我再列出我的职业资格证书吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Would you like me to list my professional credentials again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.71,0:13:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,喝咖啡吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.34,0:13:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你能别动了吗  你让我的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Can you stop moving? You're taking my nerves over the edge
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.13,0:13:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,焦虑指数爆表了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}to a proverbial 11 on a scale of 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.34,0:13:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我控制不了  我们一直在等\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I can't help it. We've been waiting and waiting,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我真的好想解手\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and now I have to pee really, really bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.18,0:14:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我不该提的  我马上回来\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I shouldn't have mentioned it. Be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.06,0:14:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不  别分开了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No! No! No more splitting up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.60,0:14:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,尤金  既然那个穿着橙色服装的帅哥\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Eugene. If that fine-ass dude in the orange suit
