Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.53,0:14:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那由美子的情况肯定很好  对吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}things must be going good for Yumiko, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.86,0:14:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我回来时她就出来了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Maybe she'll be out by the time I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.16,0:14:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰了[以下为西语]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么能帮你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.66,0:14:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我能去外面解手的那个洞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.33,0:14:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以去这里的洗手间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.17,0:14:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,什么洗手间  这里有洗手间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.55,0:14:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,进去  右拐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.22,0:14:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.59,0:14:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,有卫生纸吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Uh, do you have toilet paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.76,0:14:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,该死\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Well, shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.81,0:14:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我好激动\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'm excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,听我数  三二一\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}On my count. 3, 2, 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.55,0:15:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你们去解决那个吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Why don't you guys handle that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.93,0:16:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你们累了  我们就接手\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}If you get tired out, we'll take over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.14,0:16:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是顶上传来的声音吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Is that the roof?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.65,0:16:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是行尸\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Could be walkers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.65,0:16:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,声音是下面传来的  是摩斯电码\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It's below us. It's Morse code.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,意思是救命\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It's SOS.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我滑倒了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I slipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.64,0:16:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他看见了  却留下我等死\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}He saw, and he left me to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.19,0:16:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.65,0:16:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  那又如何\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Okay. So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.57,0:16:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你就直接承认了吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You're just admitting it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.20,0:17:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你想杀了她\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You tried to kill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.49,0:17:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不  她有麻烦了  我没帮忙\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No, she was in trouble, and I didn't help.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.28,0:17:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这两者区别很大\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}There is a big difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.71,0:17:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  现在谁会帮你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Okay, so who's gonna help you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.62,0:17:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这里有谁会支持你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Who in here's got your back?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.17,0:17:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不用手指也能数出那个数\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Yeah, you don't need fingers to count that number.
