Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.80,0:17:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,就因为我没有为她冒生命危险吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}'cause I didn't risk my nuts for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.81,0:17:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我为你们每个人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I have been a golden goddamn asset
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.73,0:17:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,都提供了巨大的帮助\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}for every single one of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.19,0:17:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  烧掉山顶寨也有帮助  对吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Yeah, burning Hilltop, that helped, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.19,0:17:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我杀了阿尔法  对吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I killed Alpha, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.02,0:17:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,所以没错  是有帮助\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}So, yeah, I was helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,因为如果我没那样做\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}'Cause if I hadn't done that,
