Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.58,0:17:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我做了必须做的事  好吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I did what needed to be done, alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.08,0:17:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我有在努力\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I am trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.62,0:17:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我一个字也不信\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Yeah, okay. I'm not buying a word of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.38,0:17:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Same.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.21,0:17:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,点点头  我就动手\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Nod and it happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.17,0:17:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,没有他  我们也能穿过城市\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We can get through the city without him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.84,0:18:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,救命  救救我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Help! Help me! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.18,0:18:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,-回头再说  -救命\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- Later. - Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.31,0:18:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,救命\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.23,0:18:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,盖奇  发生了什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Gage?! What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.94,0:18:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在隧道里迷路了  到处都是行尸\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We got lost in the tunnels! Walkers are everywhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.69,0:18:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,-它们也许...  -你怎么进去的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- they -- they might have -- - How'd you get in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.99,0:18:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我打开了远端的一扇门\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I-I got a door open on the far end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.78,0:18:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你关了门吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Did you close it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.49,0:18:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-盖奇  -我...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- Gage? - I --
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.28,0:18:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这玩意儿似乎松动了  大脚怪  帮帮忙\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Hey, this one seems a bit looser. Sasquatch, gimme a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.83,0:18:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要是开门  行尸会一拥而入\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We open that, they'll all get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.91,0:18:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他就在我们眼前\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}He's right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.96,0:18:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I know he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.13,0:18:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,去你的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}The hell with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.59,0:18:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,奥尔登\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Alden?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.55,0:18:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,快啊\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.51,0:18:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你疯了吗  让开\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Are you insane? Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.05,0:18:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,让开\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.72,0:18:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,玛姬\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Maggie?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.43,0:18:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,玛姬\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Maggie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.23,0:18:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,开门\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.31,0:18:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉  好吗  对不起\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Look, I'm sorry, okay?! I'm sorry --
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.69,0:18:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我犯了个错  对不起\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I made -- I made a mistake, and I'm sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.73,0:19:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,但我只是\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}but I just --
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.82,0:19:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,再给我一次机会  好吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I want another chance. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.86,0:19:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会再这样做了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I won't do it again. I won't do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.53,0:19:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我会表现更好  求你了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'll do better. Please, I -- Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.37,0:19:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,玛姬  听我说\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Maggie, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.08,0:19:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有时间  我们可以打开那扇门\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We have time. We can get that door open.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,玛姬  玛姬\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Maggie! Maggie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.67,0:19:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没有足够的弹药杀掉它们\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We don't have the ammo to clear them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.47,0:19:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,放手吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.89,0:19:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.72,0:19:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能开门\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.69,0:19:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,骗子\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.33,0:21:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰了  我在等我的朋友  由美子\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Pardon me. I've been waiting for my friend, Yumiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.21,0:21:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,她就在那个房间里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}She's in that room right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.04,0:21:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,请问你能否告知我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I was wondering if you might be able to provide
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.92,0:21:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,她何时才能出来\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}or procure for me an ETA for when she might be done?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.21,0:21:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,里面没人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No one's in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.22,0:21:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但我看着我的朋友和两个提问人进去了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}But I watched my friend walk in there with the two questioners,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.22,0:21:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我没见到她或他们走出来\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and I haven't seen her or them walk out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.85,0:21:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你可以去看看\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}If you could just check --
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.72,0:21:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,里面没人  先生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No one is in there, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.35,0:21:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我的另一个朋友去女厕所了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}My other friend went to use the ladies' room --
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.10,0:21:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,什么朋友\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}What friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.15,0:21:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我得请你离开了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I need you to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.07,0:21:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,立刻\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.11,0:22:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.15,0:22:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕的回忆\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Bad memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.57,0:22:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,什么回忆\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.83,0:23:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你们不愿意看他\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You guys don't wanna look at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.79,0:23:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.04,0:23:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你们为什么不看他\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Why won't you look at him?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.75,0:23:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那不过是一副空皮囊  他死得像个懦夫\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}All that is, is the shell of a man who died a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.80,0:23:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,真会说啊  神父\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}That's a hot take, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.68,0:23:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他确实是怕了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}He was scared,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.14,0:23:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,但他不该那样死去\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}but he didn't deserve to die like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.27,0:23:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那是最糟糕的死法\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}In the worst way imaginable.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.94,0:23:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,有更糟糕的死法\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}There are worse ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.15,0:23:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕得多\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}A lot worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.29,0:24:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,在我找到伊莱哲和他的人之前\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Before I found Elijah and his people...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.84,0:24:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,赫谢尔和我单独生活了很久\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Hershel and I were alone for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.34,0:24:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,有一天  我们碰到了一个虚弱的老人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}One day, we came across this frail old man
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.56,0:24:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他跪在一个翻倒的超市购物车旁边\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}who was kneeling by a turned-over grocery cart.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.94,0:24:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,里面全是找来的衣服\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It was full of scavenged clothes
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.85,0:24:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他说是给他的儿女们穿的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}he said were for his sons and daughters,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.27,0:24:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,问我们能否帮他把车拉回去\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and could we help him haul the cart back home?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.86,0:24:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他说他会给我们食物来补偿\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And he said he'd give us food for our trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.37,0:24:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道他是个骗子\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I knew that he was a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.50,0:24:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但我很饿\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}But I was starving,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.67,0:24:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不久后  赫谢尔也会挨饿\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and soon, Hershel would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.21,0:24:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们跟着他去了他家\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}So we followed him back to his house.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.51,0:24:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我用刀抵着他的脖子  搜了他的口袋\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I held a knife to his throat and reached in his pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.76,0:25:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我掏出了他原本用来迷晕我的氯仿布\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I pulled out the chloroform rag he was gonna use on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.18,0:25:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,塞在了他的嘴里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I stuffed it in his mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.14,0:25:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我们进了房子\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And then we went inside the house,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.40,0:25:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我把儿子锁在一个房间里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and I locked my little boy in a room,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.44,0:25:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,然后去探索房子\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and I went and searched the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.53,0:25:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那里有三个\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}There were these three...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.91,0:25:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,畸形的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}deformed --
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.75,0:25:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我都不会称他们为人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I wouldn't call them men.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.92,0:25:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他们冲着我来了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}They came after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.55,0:25:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,但我解决了他们\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}But I handled them.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.89,0:25:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,然后整个房子都安静了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And then the house was quiet,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.52,0:25:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,只剩下楼上\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}except for this thudding sound
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.27,0:25:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,阁楼里传来的砰砰声\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}that was coming from upstairs in the attic.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.28,0:26:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为楼上有人被绑了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And I thought maybe they had people tied up up there
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.82,0:26:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他们想逃跑\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}that were trying to get free.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.95,0:26:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我走到走廊尽头的一扇门前\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}So I walked to a door at the end of this hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.83,0:26:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我打开门  抬头看\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And I opened it, and I looked up,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.29,0:26:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那里有一排楼梯\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and there was a set of stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.71,0:26:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,在楼梯顶部有个影子\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}At the top of the stairs, there's this shadow
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.76,0:26:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,在扭动和摇摆\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}writhing and rocking.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.22,0:26:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为是个动物\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I thought it was an animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.60,0:26:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,突然间  它从楼梯上掉了下来\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Then all of a sudden, it fell down the stairs,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.73,0:26:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,落在了我的脚边\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and it came right at my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.32,0:26:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那是个行尸\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It was a walker
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.78,0:26:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,曾经是个女人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}that used to be a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.99,0:26:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,她的胳膊和腿\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Her arms and her legs
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.08,0:26:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,都被砍掉了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}had been cut off,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.29,0:26:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,缝合了伤口\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}stitched up.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.67,0:26:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,她的眼睛被挖掉了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Her eyes gouged out.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.46,0:27:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,没有舌头\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.09,0:27:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,她在呼呼喘息\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And she was wheezing
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.01,0:27:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,透过喉咙上敞开的  被灼烧过的伤口\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}through an open, cauterized gash in her throat
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.68,0:27:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,她的声带被扯掉了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}where her vocal cords had been ripped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.48,0:27:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,她的肚子又大又圆\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And her belly was round and full.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.11,0:27:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,里面的那个东西想要破肚而出\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And whatever was inside of there was trying to get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.12,0:27:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我走上楼  楼上有三个像她一样的人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And I went upstairs, and there were three more just like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.62,0:27:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,但她们依然有心跳\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}But their hearts were still beating.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.75,0:27:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我当时的第一个想法是什么吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And do you know the first thing I thought?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.05,0:27:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我所想到的第一件事是什么吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}The very first thing that crossed my mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.05,0:27:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,"既然她们活着\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}"If they're alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.47,0:27:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那这里一定有食物"\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}there must be food here."
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.52,0:27:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我解决了她们\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}So I took care of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.69,0:27:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,然后找到了食物\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And then I found the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.65,0:28:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,非常多的食物\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Lots of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.57,0:28:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,赫谢尔和我装满了购物车  然后走了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And Hershel and I filled the cart with it, and we left.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.96,0:28:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,在告诉你这件事时  我没有任何情绪\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I don't feel anything when I tell you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.96,0:28:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你懂我的意思吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Do you understand me?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.43,0:28:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,因为外面就是这样的世界\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Because that is what's out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.06,0:28:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,看到那一幕  让我失去了某些东西\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And seeing it, I lost something.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.73,0:28:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,而我认为失去那些东西不是件坏事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And I don't think it's a bad thing that I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.81,0:28:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这让一切变得清晰多了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Because it has made things so much clearer.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.65,0:28:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在亚历山大\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}What we have in Alexandria,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.11,0:28:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,在山顶寨和子午镇\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}what we had in Hilltop
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.83,0:28:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,所拥有的一切\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and in Meridian --
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.75,0:28:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,非常稀有\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}it's rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.46,0:28:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,一定如此\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It has to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.34,0:29:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,与外面的一切相比起来\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Compared to everything that's out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.47,0:29:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,因为如果不是的话...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Because if it isn't --
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.80,0:29:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这意味着我们很走运\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It means we were lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.89,0:29:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这意味着没人搞清楚了该做什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It means that nobody has it figured out.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.81,0:29:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,以前没人搞清楚\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Nobody ever did,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.48,0:29:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,以后也不会有人搞清楚\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and nobody ever will.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.03,0:30:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,狗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.00,0:31:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,达里尔  救救我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Daryl, help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.04,0:31:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,有多严重\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}How bad is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.25,0:31:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不乐观\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It ain't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.92,0:31:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你去上面了吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You went topside?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.59,0:31:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.30,0:31:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,坏主意\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Bad idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.43,0:32:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我和盖奇走散了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I lost Gage.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.68,0:32:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,弹药包呢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Where's the ammo bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.81,0:32:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,弹药包呢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Where's the ammo bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.85,0:32:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我也弄丢了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I lost that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.95,0:32:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,别  住手\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Don't -- Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.11,0:32:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,别浪费在我身上\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Don't waste that on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.74,0:32:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,给  我只有这些了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Here. It's all I got.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.71,0:32:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我的孩子们  我没有像懦夫一样死去\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Tell my kids I didn't die a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.20,0:32:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,卡住了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It's blocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.51,0:35:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,它们从这边来了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}They're coming in from this side!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.78,0:35:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,退后\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Back up!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.82,0:36:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,嘘  小子\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Shh, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.09,0:37:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,快  再挪开点\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Come on, little more!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.55,0:37:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,快点\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.05,0:37:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,快走\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Come on, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.56,0:37:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,找掩护\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Get behind something!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.61,0:39:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你们把我的旅伴们怎么了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}What have you done with my traveling companions?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.03,0:39:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他们正在被评估处理\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}They're being processed.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.62,0:39:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是指行政上的"评估"\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}"Processed" as in a-administratively?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.41,0:39:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,还是像红肠或其他肉一样被"处理"了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}"Processed" as in bologna or other meat stuffs?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.71,0:39:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我的好奇心需要得到答案\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}This inquiring mind needs to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.75,0:39:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我要见他们\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I want to see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.71,0:39:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢紧张吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You like feeling nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.05,0:39:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不喜欢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.43,0:39:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,只有一件事能让我紧张起来\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Only one thing gets my heart up.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.26,0:39:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,当我在外面\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}When I'm out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.56,0:39:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,与死尸战斗时\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}battling the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.81,0:39:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,心潮澎湃\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}The magenta swarms.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.23,0:39:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,真是...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.65,0:39:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,每一次都血脉偾张\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}pumping, every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.45,0:39:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,但这不是坏事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}But not in a bad way.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.04,0:40:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,给  擦干净\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Here. Mop up.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.84,0:40:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,-我认为...  -你屁谎都不会说\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I-I think that -- You can't lie for shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.47,0:40:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,-我...   -所以别说了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I -- So don't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.18,0:40:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好  我没打算说谎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Okay. I wasn't g-going to.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.48,0:40:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,没打算啊\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You weren't?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.77,0:40:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.02,0:40:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那我对你有好感了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}That makes me like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.90,0:40:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,继续保持下去  能帮到你自己\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Keep doing that, it'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.40,0:40:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不这样...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}If you don't --
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.99,0:40:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你懂吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You get me?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.95,0:40:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,大声说出来\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Use your words.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.50,0:40:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,懂  我懂  长官\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Y-Yes. Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.71,0:40:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.17,0:40:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,现在\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.75,0:40:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你有所隐瞒\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I know you're holding back.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.01,0:40:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道你有所隐瞒\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You know you're holding back.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.18,0:40:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我会问你两个问题\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'm going to give you two questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.97,0:41:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你要给我两个回答  真实的回答\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You're going to give me two answers. Truthful ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.68,0:41:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,做到这点\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.10,0:41:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你就能走\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You get to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.81,0:41:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你就能再次见到你的朋友们\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You get to see your friends again.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.52,0:41:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都会好起来\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Everything will be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.44,0:41:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,就这么简单\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It's that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.24,0:41:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.78,0:41:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的社区在哪里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Where is your settlement?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.08,0:41:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你们为什么去那个火车站\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And why were you at that train station?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.50,0:41:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,尤金\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Mm, Eugene.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.00,0:41:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你说谎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}If you lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.17,0:41:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我会知道的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'll know.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.63,0:41:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}O-Okey-dokey.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.06,0:41:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你说得对\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.39,0:41:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我的确隐瞒了一些事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I have been holding something back.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.02,0:41:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,实话说  我之前就想说出来\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Frankly, I wanted to speak up before this,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.02,0:41:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,但我担心我的朋友们会不满\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}but I was afraid of what my friends would think.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.07,0:42:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前不是个感情外露的人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I haven't always been the most emotional fella,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.53,0:42:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,但一万小时以上的死亡  失去和恐惧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}but my 10,000-plus hours of death, loss, and fear
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.83,0:42:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,让我敞开了一点心扉\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}have opened me up a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.91,0:42:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,在我们的旅途中  我发现了一台无线电\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}In the course of our travels, I found this radio.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.09,0:42:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,每天晚上  我都对着虚空说话\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Night after night, I would speak into the void,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.13,0:42:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,期待着"假如"发生\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}holding onto a-a "what if,"
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.80,0:42:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这是愚人的做法  而我只是个愚人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}as fools are wont to do, and I am nothing if not a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.81,0:42:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,然后一天晚上\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Then one night,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.15,0:42:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,虚空中传回了一个声音\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}a voice came back from said void.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.82,0:42:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,一个动听的声音\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}A beautiful voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.90,0:42:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们聊了起来  而她...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We got to talking, and she...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.41,0:42:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不反感我的想法\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}...was not repulsed by my musings.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.37,0:42:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我们聊到了火车博物馆和冰淇淋甜筒\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We spoke of train museums and ice cream cones.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.84,0:42:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我们欢笑\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We laughed.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.09,0:43:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我们唱了铁娘子乐队的歌\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We sang Iron Maiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.18,0:43:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我们想见面\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And then we wanted to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.97,0:43:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我叫上了朋友们\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}So I got my friends
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.97,0:43:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,去了那个火车场  假装可以\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}to go to that train yard under the guise
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.44,0:43:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,求出现在那里的人帮助我们三人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}of asking whoever showed up for help for us three,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.60,0:43:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我知道不然他们是不会去的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}because I knew they wouldn't go otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.65,0:43:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,但我的脑子里只有史蒂芬妮\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}But all I was thinking about was Stephanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.40,0:43:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,所以没错  我说谎了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}So yes, I lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.24,0:43:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直在说谎  因为我害怕失去\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I've been lying this whole time, because I'm afraid to lose
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.49,0:43:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我在这世界上仅剩的三个朋友\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}the three friends I have in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.58,0:43:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我骗史蒂芬妮说我来自一个大社区\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And I lied to Stephanie about being from a large settlement
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.17,0:43:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我害怕也许\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}because I was afraid that maybe,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.46,0:43:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,她不是她所说的那个人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}she was not who she said she was.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.88,0:43:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,也许这是个美人计\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}That maybe she was a femme fatale,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.88,0:43:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,专给孤独之人下套\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}laying a trap for a lonely heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.80,0:43:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我在恋爱方面向来一塌糊涂\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}My track record in the romantic realm is spotty at best.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.68,0:43:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我与任何人都搞不好关系\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'm not one for whom any relationships come easy,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.06,0:43:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其是与异性佳人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}particularly those with the fairer sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.69,0:44:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我其实还是个处男\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And I am, in fact, a virgin.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.11,0:44:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管我曾多次观察过房事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Even though I have, uh, observed the act
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.07,0:44:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,次数多到我都不好意思承认了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}far more times than I care to admit.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.41,0:44:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢你们忍住了嘲笑\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Thank you for holding back your titters.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.58,0:44:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我本希望\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I was -- I was hoping
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.96,0:44:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,在经过适度追求后\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}that after a suitable period of courtship,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.71,0:44:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,史蒂芬妮也许能改变我这难堪的状态\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}that Stephanie might be the one to change my unenviable status,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.26,0:44:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我在内心深处希望\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}because deep down, I was hoping that maybe, in fact,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.43,0:44:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,她是我的一生真爱\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}she was my One True Love.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.97,0:44:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我被迫在这个房间里承认了这件事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And now I've been forced to admit that in this room,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.27,0:44:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这让我羞耻万分\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and I'm humiliated by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.27,0:44:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,而且\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.06,0:44:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我害怕如果史蒂芬妮知道了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'm afraid that if Stephanie finds out
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.86,0:44:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我没对她说实话\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}that I wasn't honest with her, either,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.61,0:44:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,她就永远不理我了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}that she might want to have nothing to do with me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.41,0:44:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我在这里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}So here I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.04,0:44:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,坦白了这件事  长舒了一口气\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}very relieved to get that off my chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.17,0:44:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,因为除此之外  我至今为止说的每句话\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Because everything else I've said up to this point
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.00,0:45:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,都他妈的是真话\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}has been the goddamn truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.76,0:45:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,尤金\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Eugene!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.02,0:46:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,没事了  哥们  哭出来\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It's okay, man. Let it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.86,0:46:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为...  他们带你们去了哪里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I thought -- W-Where'd they take you?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.12,0:46:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,一个医务室\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}An infirmary.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.37,0:46:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,有个医生给我做了雾疗  给了我难喝的草药止咳糖浆\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}A medic steamed my face, gave me this nasty herbal cough syrup,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.33,0:46:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我睡着了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and I slept.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.58,0:46:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在糖浆里下药了吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}They spiked the cough syrup?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.25,0:46:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不是  他们麻醉了我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No, no. They took the lantern out of my room,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.67,0:46:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我入睡了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and I fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.88,0:46:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,医生检查了我几次\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Medic checked on me a couple of times,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.17,0:46:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,然后他们带由美子来看了我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and then they brought Yumiko to visit,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.80,0:46:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,然后带我们去等待室见了公主\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and then they took us to a holding room with Princess,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.93,0:46:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,然后带我们来了这里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and then they brought us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.93,0:46:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,对  谢天谢地你也来了  我们很担心你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Yeah. Thank God you're here, too. We were worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.15,0:46:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,根据《新永久联合条例》第114A节\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Pursuant to Section 114A of the New Articles of Perpetual Union,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.65,0:46:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,遵从《原宪法》第1条第8节\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}in deference to traditions established by Article 1,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.16,0:46:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,《原世界人权宣言》第14条\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Section 8 of the Legacy Constitution
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.37,0:46:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,所确立的传统\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and Article 14 of the Legacy UDHR,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.37,0:47:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你们已成功通过了在此联合城镇\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}you have successfully completed initial processing
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.25,0:47:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,获得庇护和公民权的初步评估\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}in consideration for asylum and citizenship in these united townships.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.88,0:47:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,在你们穿过这些门后\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}When you walk through these doors,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.84,0:47:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,将有"片警"护送你们\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}you'll be escorted to orientation.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.68,0:47:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,去参加迎新\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}By a beat cop.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.22,0:47:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到联邦\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Welcome to the Commonwealth.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.15,0:47:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我上的是西点军校  混蛋\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I went to West Point, asshole.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.69,0:47:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我不懂  有什么变了  他们为什么突然...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I don't get it. What the hell changed? Why did they all --
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.65,0:47:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,别质疑了  我们进去了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Don't question it. We're in.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.46,0:47:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你们哪位是尤金\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Which one of you is Eugene?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.26,0:47:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我是史蒂芬妮\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'm Stephanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.79,0:48:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9\bord1\fs14\b1\frz59\pos(215,70)\fn华文中宋}迪加德东市场站
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.58,0:49:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.75,0:49:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,一个孩子给他父母写的信\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It's a letter from this kid to his parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.79,0:49:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,过去的东西\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It's from back before.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.50,0:49:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你找到的吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You found it?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.00,0:49:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  在隧道里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Yeah, down in the tunnels.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.42,0:49:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,在下面看到别的东西了吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}See anything else down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.84,0:49:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,没有  跟你看到的一样\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Nah. Just the same stuff you saw.
